{"type": "article", "id": 16873, "title": "关于美国青少年们买买买的 14 条真相", "description": "看出来了吗？虽然大品牌还是一统天下，小众和个性产品崛起的速度越来越快了。", "date": "2015-11-01T08:12:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 717, "name": "消费"}], "category": 18, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 141, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144345TfJOzltXVIF6sREa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.piperjaffray.com/2col.aspx?id=287&amp;releaseid=2097002&amp;title=More+Denim%2c+Netflix+and+YouTube%3b+Less+Handbags+and+Broadcast+Media%2c+According+to+Survey+of+9%2c400+Teens\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-align:left;\">美国咨询公司 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">Piper Jaffray  </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">从</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> 2001 </span></a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><a href=\"http://www.piperjaffray.com/2col.aspx?id=287&amp;releaseid=2097002&amp;title=More+Denim%2c+Netflix+and+YouTube%3b+Less+Handbags+and+Broadcast+Media%2c+According+to+Survey+of+9%2c400+Teens\" target=\"_blank\">年开始</a><span></span>，每半年发布一次青少年消费趋势研究报告。以下数据来自他们的第</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> 30 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">份报告，一共调查了</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> 9400 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">位青少年。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1. 时尚。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> 总的来说，青少年们的消费总额在下降，也就是说花钱花少了。但是富裕的同学，不管是家里富还是自己会赚，他们时尚开销越来越大。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144336D1ilu7FqmK9GwkT5.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.54\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2. 牛仔布/丹宁布。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>牛仔布</span>越来越受欢迎，相应下降的是快速时尚业。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061443375GofFCQ9us0ize6Z.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>3. 运动服。 </strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t还是很爱运动服装。<span>Nike </span>最受欢迎。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144338r9tBQdNEIj1Zl4vM.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong> 4. 更少的包包。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t女孩们今年在配饰上的消费下降了４％——买更少的包包。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144339NSch5qjFGbrDQd2s.gif\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>5.  独立品牌。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t化妆品方面，独立的小品牌在抢占大品牌的市场。因为现在强调个性，而不再是跟大家一样。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144129pd9JS3rVY4Bh0NbO.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"264\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>6.  特色小店。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t女孩们花更多的时间逛特色小店而不是大商场，已经占到购物时间的 <span>33 </span>％，每年增长<span> 5%</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144339HXrp1wu8y3DEzBUe.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>7. Netflix </strong></span><span><strong>和</strong></span><span><strong> Youtube 。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t总的来说，大家 <span>59% </span>的时间是在 <span>Netflix </span>和<span> Youtube </span>上看视频，但还有 <span>29% </span>的时间在看电视。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144340M1WfEt59YkI3sFhL.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8. 青春片、科幻片。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t今年最受期待的电影是：《饥饿游戏<span>3： </span>嘲笑鸟<span>(</span>下<span>)</span>》、《星球大战<span> 7</span>：原力觉醒》、《分歧者》。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144341c9nK2NbCaRrtZQOB.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>9.  </strong><span><strong>Spotify。</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t没人听广播了，都在听在线音乐。<span>Spotify </span>正在威胁 <span>Pandora</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144342lkuWKG3M5hrZBgaR.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.6672\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>10. Amazon。 </strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t最受欢迎的购物网站：<span>Amazon 38%</span>，<span>Nike 8%</span>，<span>eBay 4%</span>，<span>Forever 21 3%, Urban Outfitters 3%</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144342EnNe8BYKUIPRjzvV.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>11. Nike。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t最受欢迎的服装品牌：<span>Nike 27%, Forever 21 7%, American Eagle 6%, Ralph Lauren 5%, Urban\r\nOutfitters 3%</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144343DJ0ZxNGuyaAMtPeE.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>12. </strong><span><strong>Michale Kors 。</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t最受欢迎的包包品牌：<span>Michale Kors 31%</span>，<span>Kate Spade 15%</span>，<span>Coach 10%</span>，<span> Louits Vuitton 6%</span>，<span>Vera Bradley 5%</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061443448szqOS3WaVUbyC0Z.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.74657534\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>13. 还是 </strong><span><strong>Nike。</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t最受欢迎的鞋品牌：<span>Nike 50%</span>，<span>Vans 9%</span>，<span>Converse 7%</span>，<span>Sperry Top-Sider 4%</span>，<span>Steven Madden 3%</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144344aZJ1p3stdGQBmTfN.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.524\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span><strong>14.  </strong><span><strong>MAC 。</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span>最受欢迎的化妆品品牌：<span>MAC，</span>美宝莲，<span>Urban Decay</span>，<span>Cover Girl</span>，<span>Bare Escentuals</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144345KhScHGnzB2TIdi4u.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://giphy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">giphy.com</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}